title: Saxony Landtag Elections
new-page: true
tags: event
priority: -2
view-if: (year = saxony_election_year and month >= saxony_election_month) or (year > saxony_election_year)
on-departure: saxony_election_year = saxony_election_year + 4 if saxony_snap_election_called == 0; saxony_election_year = year + 4 if saxony_snap_election_called == 1; saxony_election_month = month if saxony_snap_election_called == 1; saxony_snap_election_called = 0
set-jump: saxony_landtag_results

= Saxony Landtag Elections, [+ month : month +] [+ year +]

Saxony holds Landtag elections. This system reuses federal party support, applies Saxony weights and the SPD/ASPD split rules, normalizes results, and allocates **96** seats with D'Hondt.

- @calculate_saxony_landtag: Count the votes.

@calculate_saxony_landtag
on-arrival: saxony_government = 1 if saxony_government == undefined; saxony_majority_cabinet = 0 if saxony_majority_cabinet == undefined
go-to: election_algorithm
set-jump: saxony_landtag_results

@saxony_landtag_results
on-arrival: {! var isSaxonySnapElection = Number(Q.saxony_snap_election_called) === 1; Q.saxony_next_election_year_preview = (isSaxonySnapElection ? (Number(Q.year) || 0) : (Number(Q.saxony_election_year) || Number(Q.year) || 0)) + 4; Q.saxony_next_election_month_preview = isSaxonySnapElection ? Q.month : Q.saxony_election_month; if (typeof window !== 'undefined' && typeof window.calculateSaxonyLandtagResults === 'function') { window.calculateSaxonyLandtagResults(Q); } if (typeof window !== 'undefined' && typeof window.updateSaxonyCoalitionOptions === 'function') { window.updateSaxonyCoalitionOptions(Q); } !}

= Saxony Landtag election results

Next Saxony election after this Landtag is due in **[+ saxony_next_election_month_preview : month +] [+ saxony_next_election_year_preview +]**.

Saxony Landtag seats: **[+ saxony_landtag_total_seats +] / 96**

Current Saxony government: **[+ saxony_current_government_name +]** ([+ saxony_current_government_parties +]).

Current government seats: **[+ saxony_current_government_seats +] / 96**. Status: **[+ saxony_current_government_status +]**. Majority cabinet: **[+ saxony_majority_cabinet +]**.

Current government leverage: **[+ saxony_leverage +]**.

= Choose a Saxony coalition

A coalition is selectable if it controls at least **49** of the **96** Landtag seats. If no listed coalition has a majority, the incumbent Saxony government may continue as a minority cabinet.

- @saxony_select_kpd_spd
- @saxony_select_spd_aspd_ddp
- @saxony_select_spd_aspd_ddp_dvp
- @saxony_select_aspd_dvp_ddp_wp_dnvp
- @saxony_select_dvp_wp_dnvp_nsdap
- @new_saxony_elections: Call new Saxony Landtag elections.
- @root: Continue without changing the Saxony government.

